{"tid":2248064,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"本港增4宗確診無源頭不明 政府稱完成籌備「健康碼」","createTime":"2020-10-18T10:20:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T11:16:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"e79ba10deaaf13b96fec73b38540f80d0b2b0b46","tid":2248064,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:20:00.000Z","msg":"本港增4宗確診無源頭不明 政府稱完成籌備「健康碼」<br />\n<br />\n本港新增4宗新型肺炎確診個案，無不明源頭感染。兩宗本地個案，患者分別是尖沙咀帝苑酒店及殘疾人士院舍國寶之家的員工。另外兩宗是輸入個案。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府在梁顯利油麻地社區中心設立臨時檢測中心，今日最後一日開放。有市民說，為了保障自己和家人，再接受檢測。<br />\n<br />\n食物及衞生局局長陳肇始說，4間臨時檢測中心累計收集超過1萬5千5百個樣本，會積極研究在個案或群組較多的地區，設臨時檢測中心，又說當局已完成「健康碼」的籌備工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555400-20201018.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555400-20201018.htm&d=89HDPkshzIuckIexGTa1a4tKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=14205f10\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1555400-20201018.htm&h=561c2c5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1555400-20201018.htm</a>"},{"pid":"211f2e685cad6f28ccba17e575957c01d12095df","tid":2248064,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:20:34.000Z","msg":"健康鹿要來了"},{"pid":"f2926061912a3f03ce6f8238db86cae31b5d36d8","tid":2248064,"uid":20689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:21:12.000Z","msg":"It&rsquo;s coming"},{"pid":"4b4d3ccf11a729966e8fa9a1fe5fabab4f67abd9","tid":2248064,"uid":3302,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:22:06.000Z","msg":"港豬基因資料庫<br />\n人臉辨識<br />\n遊行一掃到你條撚樣即刻扣一萬分<br />\n以後唔俾出境<br />\n諗起都爽<br />\n垃圾港豬抵撚死"},{"pid":"b22f3e99133febcc7e7d361c790d83f2cf00b571","tid":2248064,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T10:33:02.000Z","msg":"強制器官移植系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkg